{{Vgname|风暴英雄|en=Heroes of the Storm|tw=暴雪英霸|cn=风暴英雄}}是一款由[[暴雪娛樂|暴雪娛樂]]開發並將發佈在[[Windows|Windows]]和[[Mac_OS|Mac OS]]平台上的多人在線競技類遊戲。遊戲中玩家所扮演的英雄角色大部分来自於暴雪娛樂的其他四個遊戲系列：《[[魔獸系列|魔獸系列]]》、《[[暗黑破壞神系列|暗黑破壞神]]》、《[[星海爭霸系列|星海爭霸系列]]》和《[[鬥陣特攻|鬥陣特攻]]》，少部分來自於《[[失落的維京人|失落的維京人]]》。它是一款免费的在線遊戲，匹配系统基於暴雪的[[战网|战网]]。暴雪對其進行了限量的内测。<ref name="eurogamer-20130122">{{cite web | url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-01-21-blizzard-actively-working-on-blizzard-all-stars-so-whats-the-hold-up | title=Blizzard "actively working" on Blizzard All-Stars, so what's the hold up? | publisher=Eurogamer.net | date=2013-01-22 | first=Wesley | last=Yin-Poole | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130506043102/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-01-21-blizzard-actively-working-on-blizzard-all-stars-so-whats-the-hold-up | archivedate=2013-05-06 | deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="mlg-anaheim2012">{{cite interview |first=Dustin |last=Browder |interviewer=StarCraft: Legacy |title=Dustin Browder Interview - MLG Anaheim 2012 |url=http://sclegacy.com/news/23-sc2/1160-dustin-browder-interview-mlg-anaheim-2012 |year=2012 |month=June |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013203349/http://sclegacy.com/news/23-sc2/1160-dustin-browder-interview-mlg-anaheim-2012 |archivedate=2012-10-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>2013年8月，這款遊戲停止内测。2013年11月，暴雪正式在暴雪嘉年華上宣布2014年上線該遊戲。<ref name="atvi-q2-2013">{{cite web |url=http://diablo.somepage.com/news/1603-diablo-iii-announcement-coming-at-gamescon |title=Diablo III Announcement Coming at Gamescon - Activision Blizzard Q2 2013 earnings report details the Blizzard All-Star progress and 'Project Titan' revamp |publisher=Diablo Somepage |date=2013-08-01 |accessdate=2013-09-22 |last=Bramblet |first=Matthew |archive-date=2013-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130809012024/http://diablo.somepage.com/news/1603-diablo-iii-announcement-coming-at-gamescon |dead-url=yes }}</ref>暴雪否認自己的遊戲是“Action RTS”（DotA/DOTA 2）或者“MOBA”（[[英雄联盟|LOL]]）类型的游戏，因為暴雪認為《暴雪英霸》不同於市面上所有競技類遊戲。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/blizzard-explains-why-it-doesn-t-call-heroes-of-the-storm-a-moba/1100-6416084/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-11-11 |archive-date=2013-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131116030735/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/blizzard-explains-why-it-doesn-t-call-heroes-of-the-storm-a-moba/1100-6416084/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年1月13日暴雪開始讓玩家進行封閉內部測試，同年6月2日《暴雪英霸》正式上線並對外開放玩家下載遊玩。

==开发过程==
最开始，《风暴英雄》是《星际争霸2》中的一张地图，暴雪最开始称之为《暴雪DotA》，并且宣布会将其以地图的形式发布并作为一张《星际争霸2》的自定义地图<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/104641-BlizzCon-2010-Hands-On-Blizzard-DotA-Left-2-Die-Starjeweled | title=BlizzCon 2010: Hands-On Blizzard DotA, Left 2 Die, Starjeweled | publisher=The Escapist Magazine | date=2010-10-22 | last=Funk | first=John | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101026014811/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/104641-BlizzCon-2010-Hands-On-Blizzard-DotA-Left-2-Die-Starjeweled | archivedate=2010-10-26 | deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在2010年，暴雪首次在暴雪嘉年华中邀请玩家测试《暴雪DotA》，得到了玩家的认可和喜爱。暴雪宣称，《暴雪DotA》的理念在于“快速”和“平衡”<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AAgUx0nmgRc | title=Blizzard DotA - BlizzCon 2010 - Matt Gotcher, StarCraft II Level Designer | publisher=YouTube.com | date=2010-10-23 | accessdate=2013-03-02 | archive-date=2021-04-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414154803/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AAgUx0nmgRc | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年，暴雪宣布重新制作《暴雪DotA》，并且宣布游戏将联合暴雪战网进行开发<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-08-22-blizzard-dota-completely-rebooted | title=Blizzard DOTA "completely rebooted" | publisher=Eurogamer.net | date=2011-08-22 | accessdate=2013-03-02 | author=Yin-Poole, Wesley | archive-date=2021-02-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222011451/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-08-22-blizzard-dota-completely-rebooted | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://us.battle.net/blizzcon/en/blog/3768746/StarCraft_II_%E2%80%93_Blizzard_All_Stars__Mod_Tools_Panel-10_22_2011 | title=StarCraft II – Blizzard All Stars & Mod Tools Panel | publisher=Blizzard Entertainment | date=2011-10-22 | accessdate=2013-03-02 | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304210126/http://us.battle.net/blizzcon/en/blog/3768746/StarCraft_II_%E2%80%93_Blizzard_All_Stars__Mod_Tools_Panel-10_22_2011 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://massively.joystiq.com/2011/10/21/hands-on-with-blizzard-dota-tweaking-the-genre-blizzard-created/ | title=Hands-on with Blizzard DOTA: Tweaking the genre it created | publisher=Joystiq.com | date=2011-10-21 | accessdate=2013-03-02 | author=McCurley, Mathew | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130208162620/http://massively.joystiq.com/2011/10/21/hands-on-with-blizzard-dota-tweaking-the-genre-blizzard-created/ | archive-date=2013-02-08 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://pc.gamespy.com/pc/blizzard-dota/1210509p1.html | title=BlizzCon 2011: Blizzard DOTA Impressions | publisher=GameSpy | date=2011-10-23 | accessdate=2013-03-02 | author=Johnson, Leif | archive-date=2020-02-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200218174756/http://pc.gamespy.com/pc/blizzard-dota/1210509p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

随着[[Dota_2|DOTA 2]]的开发权被Valve夺走，暴雪夺取DOTA 2开发权的失败和收购[[Riot_Games|Riot Games]]失败，暴雪很可能会慢慢流失对抗类游戏的玩家<ref>{{cite web |last=Plunkett |first=Luke |url=http://kotaku.com/5883938/blizzard-and-valve-go-to-war-over-dota-name |title=Blizzard and Valve go to War Over DOTA Name |date=2012-02-10 |publisher=Kotaku |archivedate=2012-06-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120604075718/http://kotaku.com/5883938/blizzard-and-valve-go-to-war-over-dota-name |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2012年5月11日，Valve宣布已经将暴雪告上法庭，原因是Valve认为暴雪的《暴雪DotA》使用了DotA商标和名字，构成侵权，并提供一系列的证据显示DotA商标和名字的所有者为Valve，要求暴雪进行赔偿和道歉以及取消《暴雪DotA》，但暴雪认为DotA这个名字是属于所有玩家的，是一种游戏的类型，并不属于个人或者商业所有，但法庭宣判暴雪侵权，暴雪不得不将《暴雪DotA》改名为《暴雪全明星》。随后，暴雪对Valve进行了反击，不允许Valve在DOTA 2中使用旗下游戏人物模型和名字<ref>{{cite web |last=Reilly |first=Jim |url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2012/05/11/valve-blizzard-reach-dota-trademark-agreement.aspx |title=Valve, Blizzard Reach DOTA Trademark Agreement |date=2012-05-11 |publisher=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |archivedate=2012-07-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120724090129/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2012/05/11/valve-blizzard-reach-dota-trademark-agreement.aspx |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2012年6月，[[Dustin_Browder|Dustin Browder]]，星际争霸2的开发高管称，《暴雪全明星》因为版权和其他原因暂时不确定发布日期<ref name="mlg-anaheim2012" />。2013年1月 Browder在一次访谈中提到了《暴雪全明星》，表示这款游戏非常棒，拥有很好的游戏体验，但是这款游戏還没准备好进行玩家测试<ref name="sdclegacy-2013-01">{{cite web | url=http://sclegacy.com/site/feature/3-events/1211 | title=January 17, 2013 Dustin Browder Interview | publisher=Starcraft Legacy | date=2013-01-17 | accessdate=2013-03-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304084218/http://sclegacy.com/site/feature/3-events/1211 | archive-date=2016-03-04 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2013年2月，[[动视暴雪|动视暴雪]]公布2012年第四季度报告，其中表明《暴雪全明星》将会在2013年继续开发 <ref>{{cite web | url=http://diablo.somepage.com/news/1489-activision-blizzard-q4-2012-earnings-report | title=Activision Blizzard Q4 2012 Earnings Report | publisher=diablo.somepage.com | date=2013-02-07 | accessdate=2013-03-02 | author=Bramblet, Matthew | archive-date=2020-11-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126190752/https://diablo.somepage.com/news/1489-activision-blizzard-q4-2012-earnings-report | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年3月，Dustin Browder表示已经将一些《星际争霸2》的开发人员和美工派到了《暴雪全明星》开发组中<ref>{{cite web | url=http://us.battle.net/sc2/en/blog/8983614/Reddit_AMA_Full_Transcript-3_6_2013 | title=Reddit AMA Full Transcript - Dustin Browder, Alan Dabiri, David Kim | publisher=Blizzard Entertainment | date=2013-03-06 | accessdate=2013-03-17 | archive-date=2013-06-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130628130409/http://us.battle.net/sc2/en/blog/8983614/Reddit_AMA_Full_Transcript-3_6_2013 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年8月，暴雪娱乐创始人[[Mike_Morhaime|Mike Morhaime]]宣布《暴雪全明星》已经进入内测阶段，只有少数人参与内测。他说，《暴雪全明星》已经准备好让全世界玩家为之震惊了<ref name="atvi-q2-2013" />。2013年10月17日，《暴雪全明星》改名为《风暴英雄》<ref>{{cite web | url=http://kotaku.com/blizzard-s-diablo-starcraft-wow-crossover-has-a-new-nam-1447238984 | title=Blizzard’s Diablo/Starcraft/WoW Crossover Has a New Name | publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] | date=2013-10-17 | last=Narcisse | first=Evan | accessdate=2013-11-11 | archive-date=2013-10-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020114040/http://kotaku.com/blizzard-s-diablo-starcraft-wow-crossover-has-a-new-nam-1447238984 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。同年11月8日，Dustin Browder正式公布《风暴英雄》，并称玩家已经可以在暴雪官网上进行公测申请<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/11/08/heroes-of-the-storm-battlegrounds-revealed-beta-signups-open | title=Heroes of the Storm: Battlegrounds Revealed, Beta Signups Open | publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] | date=2013-11-08 | last=Dyer | first=Mitch | access-date=2013-11-11 | archive-date=2021-01-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124170425/https://www.ign.com/articles/2013/11/08/heroes-of-the-storm-battlegrounds-revealed-beta-signups-open | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

暴雪宣布，从2019年起，停办[[风暴英雄全球锦标赛|风暴英雄全球锦标赛]]与[[宿舍英雄|宿舍英雄]]，造成許多戰隊解散、選手失業<ref>{{cite web |title=Heroes of the Storm News . . . |url=https://news.blizzard.com/en-us/blizzard/22833558/heroes-of-the-storm-news |website=BLIZZARD |accessdate=2018-12-17 |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309103825/https://news.blizzard.com/en-us/blizzard/22833558/heroes-of-the-storm-news |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-12-22/184359 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2018-12-27 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124125405/https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2018-12-22/184359 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

